Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to exclusively offer 4-8 Ricketts Road, Mount Waverley, for lease.

Located on the door step of the diamond interchange to the Monash freeway which provides immediate access to the CBD and Eastlink making it the perfect last mile distribution centre. The facility also provides a corporate fit out with significant climate controlled infrastructure in the warehouse. 

Key Features:

- Total building area: 13,384sqm*
- Large corporate offices
- High clearance climate controlled warehouse
- Multiple production areas
- Multiple docks and roller door access
- Large power and gas available
- 225* on site car spaces
- Available October 2021

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PRIME FOOD GRADE OR LAST MILE DC

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located in the heart of the Monash commercial and industrial precinct, only 17kms* south east of the Melbourne CBD.

An opportunity, rarely offered, to occupy a facility of this quality in this highly prized location. The position offers immediate access to the M1 Freeway with the nearest on-ramp only 300m* to the north suiting warehouse and distribution businesses looking for fast and convenient access to the Melbourne CBD and surrounds.

The property comprises of 3,025sqm* of 7.6m-8m* high quality warehousing with dual roller shutter doors (7m x 6m*) providing multiple access points and goods in/out separation. 

The well-presented office/showroom is over 2 levels with both female and male amenity over both levels as well as kitchen facilities.

Additional property features include loading canopy of 65.8sqm*, significant hardstand/truck marshalling areas and ample on-site parking.

*Approx.
